The paper deals with a wireless communication system involving a UAV, which suggests that it could belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) or Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The focus on maximizing energy efficiency also suggests that it could belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) or Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Finally, the proposed method based on receding horizon optimization could also be relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
